---
// src/components/GearSection.astro
---
<section class="py-24 px-8 border-y border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">The Arsenal</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Crafting cinematic narratives requires more than just an eye; it requires precision. 
        Utilizing the <span class="text-white">Sony Alpha IV</span> and <span class="text-white">Nikon D850</span> for 
        unparalleled depth, and professional <span class="text-white">Edius</span> workflows for video.
      </p>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
        <li>• 4K Cinematic Video</li>
        <li>• Adobe Master Suite</li>
        <li>• High-Speed Primaries</li>
        <li>• 20+ Years Experience</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
       <div class="h-64 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-700">Sony A7M4</div>
       <div class="h-64 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 mt-12 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-700">D850</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>